      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="change_open_registration" data-step-uuid="959020E2-C142-46F4-BA23-AC2202668E67">
    <h2 id="change_open_registration" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Change Open Registration</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/844/650/original/c22750da-dc2b-4ec5-8636-88a5ad69f7b7.png" srcset="" alt="Change Open Registration" height="203" width="527">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_3C8D1A80-1D6F-0135-0DD6-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Settings tab under the Features heading, click the <strong>Open Registration </strong>checkbox<strong>.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Note</strong>: By default, this option is turned off. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

